Executive Profile
Brian R. Sherras  Co-Owner, Electrigen LimitedAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships59--
Background

		Mr. Brian R. Sherras serves as a Director of Sales and Business Development at Atlantic Projects Company Ltd. Mr. Sherras is responsible for Marketing and Business Development as well as Sales in Africa and the Middle East. He joined APC in 1999. he worked 18 years for GE Power Systems in various Engineering, Sales and Business Management roles. He has been a Director of Argan, Inc. (Formerly, Puroflow Inc.) since March 2012. Mr. Sherras holds a Master of Science degree ... awarded by Cranfield Institute of Technology, Bedford, England.Read Full Background




